{"type": "article", "id": 7265, "title": "Areaware 五彩缤纷的春季系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-11T07:22:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004159NsWgR4ML725wajP3.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t美国设计品牌 Areaware 发布了他们的 2015 春季系列产品。这组产品包括冰箱贴，开瓶器，手环状酒杯，拼图，扑克牌，别针和案板等。 Areaware 延续简约时尚的设计风格，同时这一季主打五彩缤纷的颜色，并且采用了更多样的材料，如瓷器，玻璃，石头甚至电线等。<a href=\"http://www.areaware.com\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看并购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004157Rt4da3chJo6xMCkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004157QKAl7YFu4GavpsVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004158UvyJ8aWh3tznrGsF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004158ZnkHVLhrJigY9IUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004159aKwARi1JmuGV58zn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}